# so_long

A 2D game project built in C using the MiniLibX graphics library. Navigate through maps, collect items, and find your way to the exit!

![Game Demo](so_long.gif)

## Table of Contents

- [About](#about)
- [Features](#features)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [Controls](#controls)
- [Map Format](#map-format)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
- [Technical Details](#technical-details)

## About

so_long is a simple 2D game where the player must collect all collectibles on the map and reach the exit with the minimum number of moves. This project is part of the 42 curriculum and focuses on window management, event handling, textures, and basic gameplay mechanics.

